{
  "texts": [
    "Specifically, the objectives of the study are delineated as follows:",
    "Examine the Applications:",
    "Identify and evaluate potential applications of GPTs in the tourism industry, focusing on key areas like personalized travel recommendations, language translation, customer service chatbots, and any other domain where natural language processing could provide value.",
    "Investigate the level of awareness, interest, and willingness among tourism professionals to adopt GPT-based solutions by analyzing survey and interview data.",
    "Discern the principal barriers inhibiting the adoption of GPTs in the industry, including technical know-how, data privacy, security concerns, and financial implications."
  ]
}